# Manual Translation Exercise

## DNA Sequence

```text
ATG GAA TTC GCT AAA TGA
```

## Translation

| Codon | Amino Acid |
| --- | --- |
| ATG | Methionine (Met) |
| GAA | Glutamic acid (Glu) |
| TTC | Phenylalanine (Phe) |
| GCT | Alanine (Ala) |
| AAA | Lysine (Lys) |
| TGA | Stop |

## Final Protein Sequence

```text
MEFAK*
```

